entries.femaleVariant: Look who's alive!
Good work, V. Old style raid!
Hey. Did you sleep all right?
Um, heh, hold up… About last night…
entries.maleVariant: Uh, hold up… About last night…

entries.femaleVariant: We don't need to talk about that.
I'm just… not like that?
So what are you like?
More like... this.
Circumstances were different, I'd say saddle up and ride after her.
But here 'n' now... Just look.
Damn hard to catch a girl like that.
Only hope you've got is they feel a pang and stop to wait.
What is with you?
Dunno. A memory, maybe. Don't matter.
Glad I could help, glad I did.
Take care of yourself.
You, too, Panam.
And remember – I'm indebted.
Ugh, OK, back to town, V. Had it up here with this gusty outback.
Next time, I choose the motel.
So-so. Back's... numb.
How's Saul?
Saul doin' all right?
Cracked skull, six busted ribs, bruised kidneys, but he's back at it, bossing folk every which way.
You?
Thought you were gonna stay with the family.
Incapable of kicking back, aren't you?
You should stay, they need you.
You gotta agree now – next time I choose the motel.
Hah, if there is such a time.
Eh, so-so. Back's strangely… numb.
entries.maleVariant: Uh, so-so. Back is strangely… numb.

entries.femaleVariant: Headin' to a ripper as soon as I'm in town. Few springs I need taken out.
entries.maleVariant: Headin' to a ripper, soon as I'm in town. Heh, few springs I need taken out.

entries.femaleVariant: Well, I slept like a puppy. That's a cozy shoulder you have there.
It's too bad I better get rolling in a minute.
Just not one to kick back and relax, are you?
It's not my style, no.
I'm back with the clan, sure, but I have things to do.
Huh, hang on. Thought you were headed back to the Aldecaldos.
entries.maleVariant: Wai... hang on. Thought you were headed back to the Aldecaldos.

entries.femaleVariant: Stayin' with the clan.
That remains so.
The Wraiths, the raid – it's the start of something we need to prepare for. Saul will get everything set in camp. Whereas I…
The Raffens wanted to know our routes, right? Well, it's the Aldecaldos' turn. Some recon is in order.
You need to stay. Think you can see that.
entries.maleVariant: You need to stay. I think you can see that.

entries.femaleVariant: Not one of them will admit it, but damn, do they need you.
entries.maleVariant: Not one of them will admit it, but – damn, do they need you.

entries.femaleVariant: Of course they do.
One more thing... Your compensation.
Please take care of her. She served me well.
Puttin' her in good hands, Panam.
I know.
Nah. Keep it.
So,uh... thank you, once again.
[Stop Panam] Wait, About last night…
Last night, when we were talking to Saul... thanks for standing up for me.
Last night, when we were talking to Saul... both of you spewed some drivel, but I do have to grant him one thing.
Come on.
Though, one thing…
Most times Saul spews drivel, mongers fear, but I have to grant him this.
Whereas you...?
Happy to help.
How're you feeling?
You bury the hatchet with Panam?
How ya feelin'?
Free.
No better feeling in the world.
I better get going.
You all bury the hatchet with Panam?
Hah. I'd say it was more like a battleax. These things, they're tough to bury and even tougher to keep buried.
But I'm optimistic. Her heart seems like it's in the right place.
Better start headin' out.
Yeah, same goes for us.
Only once the radiator gets a breather.
Thanks, V. What you did for me, I'll never forget it.
[Get up]
